# patches/0016-fetch-full-room-history.patch
#
# Epic 3: "Fetch Full History" Button per Room
#
# Provides a one-click way to aggressively fetch the entire message history
# for the current room, bypassing the standard small-chunk pagination.
#
# == Changes ==
#
# 1. src/timeline/TimelineModel.h
#    - Add Q_PROPERTY(bool fullHistoryFetching ...) for QML binding
#    - Add Q_INVOKABLE void fetchFullRoomHistory() exposed to QML
#    - Add bool fullHistoryFetching() const accessor
#    - Add fullHistoryFetchingChanged() signal
#    - Add fetchFullHistoryPage() private slot for chained HTTP fetches
#    - Add m_fullHistoryFetching boolean member
#
# 2. src/timeline/TimelineModel.cpp
#    - Implement fetchFullRoomHistory(): sets flag, kicks off chain
#    - Implement fetchFullHistoryPage(): calls /messages with limit=1000,
#      emits EventStore::oldMessagesRetrieved to reuse existing insertion
#      pipeline, chains next page via QTimer::singleShot(0, ...) to avoid
#      stack overflow and UI thread blocking.
#
# 3. resources/qml/TopBar.qml
#    - Add "Fetch Full History" MenuItem in the room options menu
#    - Show disabled + "Fetching..." text while fetch is in progress
#
